  "description": "This individual is an undead of indeterminate middle years, preserved in a state of prolonged brine-exposure that has fixed the skinTone to zombie and etched fine salt-pitting across the face and hands. Gray eyes sit deep under prominent brow ridges, and gray hair persists in sparse, stiffened strands set in a messy1 fall. The jawline remains intact but is crossed by old fracture seams that never fully knit, leaving the mouth slightly skewed at rest. The body is lean and ropey, with joint angles held in habitual tension that reads as a permanent, unyielding watchfulness.",
